Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:37.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最爱之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:42.29,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就是永远在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:45.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:50.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}让我心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:02.41,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但却难以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:12.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:17.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仍然相信命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:23.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}天空的航迹云
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:29.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}擦过天边的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:36.98,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只愿送达昔日的淡淡思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:45.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界彷如闪耀的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:55.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伴着心动的春风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:22:00.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻  好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:04.83,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:09.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但却难以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:19.47,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只愿守望你
