Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期间  也不能忘掉我校学生应有的自豪与自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome  暑假！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,60)\1c4B33D1\3c000000\bord3\fad(200,0)}剩余\N41天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,60)\1c4B33D1\3c000000\bord3}剩余\N40天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半天搞定作业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的四十天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约等于一千小时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以无尽地玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何这两天艾露希也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(1000,0)\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}（游戏任玩）
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我现在出门买游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来四十天人间蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请您不要担心  就这样  拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手  我的一千小时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来  跟客人打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马还记得吧  以前住我们隔壁的鲇川一家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马十年没见了  还记得我这个阿姨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理快看  是桂马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  都说是桂马了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打游戏打游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  这几天都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地狱开报告会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点玩游戏的时间都不给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给哥哥大人带的特产  针球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有妹妹的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾露希  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玩具真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起  我家的孩子还是这么不礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}完全没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}…也许有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  桂马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说不记得  太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  小学一年级时你俩不是同班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都只拍到了半身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  印象中是有个扭扭捏捏的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的记忆真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种场合就算忘记了也得说记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题毫不重要  我要去买游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月底再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的教育果然有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚探测器好像响了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十天  一千小时！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测器响了就有申告的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免两个恶魔同时追捕同一对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  暑假  你比任何女主角都更有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定驱魂跑进哥哥大人的青梅竹马身体里去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  竟敢妄称青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0\fad(120,0)}Flag  壹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  贰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  叁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  肆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期构建哥哥或弟弟这种恋人以下的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定过通往结局的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回忆中将要忘记一切的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了截然不同的立场再会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  那种似有似无的女人不是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  游戏里的青梅竹马可是未来的结婚对象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要随便地设定这么重要的关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是神哥哥大人忘记了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都干了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  起码先道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能扪心自问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是抱着何等的决心踏进桂木家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却一句「不记得」一笔带过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更伤人的话语了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没指望过你能帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助？帮助是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不响了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驱魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟诺拉小姐为敌是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追到这么远的地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条大鱼可不能放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是明明白白地登记了负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  接下来就轮到我们出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹马体内有驱魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说那不是青梅竹马了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就申请负责了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要我出马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这套路挺常见应该不难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是内向女孩的强烈愿望化为别的人格表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没指望过你能帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞岛学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的变化最大  跟十年前相比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中就别老是按泡沫包装纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别  别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心天理的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄安娜  为什么要把他推下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以创造和他对话的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天理在抵抗才显得这么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你要我马上说出口我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在被人追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的我能力不够  必须要依靠他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能信任桂木桂马那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他简直就是钝感的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为桂马同学一定能帮助我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理的驱魂负责人被抢先登记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人是…诺拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在我的负责地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  有其他人帮我解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  诺拉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再和桂木桂马说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将思绪投入波浪之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能获得一时的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你心灵的间隙  还是会一直残留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心灵的间隙  就由我来填补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都交给我吧  来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就听听他说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟医生问诊差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这些人就是狄安娜所说的… 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我们是你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中现在住着一个叫驱魂的坏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管就会越来越强酿成大祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要把他给淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将产生间隙的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用数倍的巨大欲望来填补的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂就会满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一万元的人就给他一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要恋人的女性就给他男公关部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受欺凌的人就给他复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的羽衣能够反映出人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就简单了  喜欢和讨厌的二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就让这个男人吃点苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉  她不是两方面都说NO了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界憎恨比爱要来得更多更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都当成憎恨的话一般都没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有听她细细道来的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  不愧是诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我可以杀了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉以快速解决闻名  试过半天内就赶出了驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  失败次数也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还试过反过头来把驱魂养大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还试过抛下协力者  自己一个人赶出驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这做法实际上是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这都是传闻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经和我无关…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底什么地方得罪你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着  通往光明未来的招待券哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公开处刑通知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心灵的间隙由我们来填补
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在海边公园  等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏  游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我要被绑着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次好像也能快速解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  还挺快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹睁大眼睛看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就让你憎恨的男人吃点苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不恨桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫描仪可不是这么说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个男人你的心灵才会产生间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个间隙里面就躲着驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉  请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是我的协力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样  这家伙就是诺拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更有蹂躏的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔复活后再收服可是禁止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原则上禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是绝对禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的协力者还不太成气候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是没办法才这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要让他比死更难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这个男人最重要的东西给毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学  我好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹  真的是小四妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于  来到结局的彼岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这就是那家伙所喜欢的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你最重要的东西给毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学是怎么看我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问  说不出口啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯说的话  我也说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂…桂…桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样  失去至爱的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取读取读取读取读取…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁  到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死小四妹的到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了煽情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者制造肤浅的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就把女主角杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有想过被你们杀掉的女主角是什么感受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把  小四妹还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心  好恶心  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  天理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人漂亮地把那两人赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让这个人来保护我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那种  像那种恶心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有活着的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊  诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是协力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档的恶魔也会一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希也会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死就死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真随便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要碰上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话能躲起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是被发现了就没地方可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要解决根本问题的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为啥非得要我保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样放着不管会很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉认为只要让哥哥大人吃苦头驱魂就会跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用别的驱魂来当作天理的驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让其被诺拉抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后被发现了也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把我被她盯上的这个状态给解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我没有能替换的驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过白亚可能有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我悠闲玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个状况了还能这么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早知道会有这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就多带几个备用电池出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像也在哪里发生过类似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就剩下两个人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是那种气氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一点勇气  天理这种时候就该…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这次逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你身上还留着驱魂那还是什么都没解决
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要依靠驱魂  自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像天理有问题似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能原谅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂就给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要依靠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我之间有什么联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也说了不记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…从来都没有忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明都不是这里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面的路你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我以前来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和桂马同学一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候也担心过电池的问题
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头看看吧  夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗星星和那颗星星和那颗星星连接在一起就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galge座了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那旁边的是美少女游戏座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再旁边的就是恋爱模拟游戏座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来很像但全部都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部连在一起成了消防车
